git stash

git stash list -----available files stash list will be reflet
git stash apply ----last stash file will be come to work space
git stash push ----file saved in stash list
git stash apply ------last stash file come to workspace
git stash drop -----last stash file come to work space and deleted the stash file in stash list
git stash pop ------at a time file come to work space and remove in status list
git stash -u -----------untraced files also stash
git stash branch brname ---------------file stash onwards create a new branch

